issue.title: Implement Admin App
issue.body:
This PR implements an server side admin app.

A flask server will serve up a set of html, js, and css files that will implement several forms for bands to register themselves and create events.
## TODO
- [x] Implement Band Form
- [x] Implement Event Form
- [ ] Query for Event Venues

@rainiera Your PR #2 should be merged first and then this code will be ready to go.

issue.title: Implement splash index front-end
issue.body:
Renders template (pure front-end) for the Museek client-side on the index (`/`) route.

Also adds emacs temps to the .gitignore.

Try it locally:
`python main.py`

Navigate to `localhost:5000`
